{"tid":682510,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[難怪養傷咁耐都未好返] 井上留下的拳王腰帶 因\"曹星如復出無期\" WBO改由2位菲律賓好手爭奪","createTime":"2018-05-29T02:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T05:47:15.000Z","uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"de6b68fa03d3fa02ed50fc5334983a549239fc4f","tid":682510,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:48:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原本就 曹狗 打排名第2條友爭<br />\n曹狗8個月都話自己未好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nWBO無奈搵第個去打<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n【WBO超蠅量級拳王之爭】世界冠軍王座戰 菲律賓兩大好手獲指名出賽<br />\n2018年05月02日 03:27 am<br />\n<br />\n腰帶唔會等人，曾經既WBO超蠅量級世界排名第1拳手曹星如復出無期，金腰帶自然由其他人爭<br />\n<br />\n日本「怪物」井上尚彌交還WBO（世界拳擊組織）超蠅量級冠軍腰帶、增磅角逐更高量級比賽，本是WBO前世界排名第1拳手、香港名將曹星如爭打金腰帶戰的機會，但自去年10月與河野公平一役受傷後，至今仍養傷復出無期，排名下降也導致失去爭拳王的機會，而WBO本周就指定目前該組織該量級世界第1、第2的菲律賓人尼迪斯（Donnie Nietes）、帕利特（Aston Palicte）爭逐世界冠軍寶座。<br />\n<br />\nWBO競賽委員會已在周一（4月30日）發信予兩名菲律賓拳手的代表，通知組織的決定並給予雙方陣營10日時間商討，以就比賽安排及細節達成協議，否則就進行競標讓各推廣公司競爭。尼迪斯上月已交還其原有的IBF（國際拳擊聯會）蠅量級冠軍腰帶冠軍腰帶，宣布減磅以爭取WBO超蠅量級冠軍腰帶，而帕利特也早已對這名銜虎視眈眈。"},{"pid":"e7fb951e042555b35ca3aa00be9826db38deeda8","tid":682510,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:48:55.000Z","msg":"條友叫<br />\n菲律賓 尼迪斯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b7f7d28feaad5b8753318226caa029ec8ec7ff6","tid":682510,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:50:02.000Z","msg":"曹狗痛哭<br />\n好想爭拳王,無奈未好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5903f5116de72e4e21fe22707bf18adef8cf609","tid":682510,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:53:26.000Z","msg":"好想挑戰井上 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ce68def54d1d04552a089276bec44023cb0037","tid":682510,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:08:28.000Z","msg":"星如或成最後贏家"},{"pid":"f2a5261430f2a08b4c1db96fd8b0459e230469f4","tid":682510,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7ce68def54d1d04552a089276bec44023cb0037","tid":682510,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:08:28.000Z","msg":"星如或成最後贏家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:14:16.000Z","msg":"緊係扮受傷啦<br />\n<br />\n唔係就要打第2名條賓仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9d2bab9ba18d27ad08be88578fc66d8b7e7fa0","tid":682510,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:15:49.000Z","msg":"君如怕一復出拎撚左腰帶就會比人挑戰<br />\n淆哂底<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4094f29a41e51b2d49eb54f9c7181c1d0e6d43","tid":682510,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:39:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7963071730349dd6b1cd17e91c76d2584c3fd90d","tid":682510,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T04:09:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcbc7fef8df370132c31a3476e569dcb4deaf87c","tid":682510,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}